Create new tidders with the provided `text/fountain` type.
Write your screenplay text in the elegant and simple [[Fountain syntax|https://fountain.io/syntax/]]

The plugin will render an approximation of the screenplay.

You can embed your fountain tiddlers in normal tiddlers using basic transclussion.

